#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.where.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.where"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.where.where:1 of
msgid "Replace values where the condition is False."
msgstr "替换条件为 False 的值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.where.where of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.where.where:3 of
msgid ""
"Where `cond` is False, keep the original value. Where True, replace with "
"corresponding value from `other`. If `cond` is callable, it is computed "
"on the Series/DataFrame and should return boolean Series/DataFrame or "
"array. The callable must not change input Series/DataFrame (though pandas"
" doesn't check it)."
msgstr ""
"当 `cond` 为 False 时，保留原始值。当为 True 时，使用 `other` 中对应的值"
"进行替换。如果 `cond` 是可调用对象，则在 Series/DataFrame 上计算，并应"
"返回布尔型 Series/DataFrame 或数组。该可调用对象不得更改输入的 Series/"
"DataFrame（尽管 pandas 不会检查）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.where.where:9 of
msgid ""
"Entries where `cond` is True are replaced with corresponding value from "
"`other`. If other is callable, it is computed on the Series/DataFrame and"
" should return scalar or Series/DataFrame. The callable must not change "
"input Series/DataFrame (though pandas doesn't check it)."
msgstr ""
"当 `cond` 为 True 时，使用 `other` 中对应的值进行替换。如果 `other` 是可"
"调用对象，则在 Series/DataFrame 上计算，并应返回标量或 Series/DataFrame。"
"该可调用对象不得更改输入的 Series/DataFrame（尽管 pandas 不会检查）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.where.where:15 of
msgid "Whether to perform the operation in place on the data."
msgstr "是否在数据上就地执行操作。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.where.where:17 of
msgid "Alignment axis if needed."
msgstr "如需对齐的轴。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.where.where:19 of
msgid "Alignment level if needed."
msgstr "如需对齐的级别。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.where.where of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.where.where:26 of
msgid ":func:`DataFrame.mask`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.where.where:27 of
msgid "Return an object of same shape as self."
msgstr "返回与自身形状相同的对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.where.where:30 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.where.where:31 of
msgid ""
"The mask method is an application of the if-then idiom. For each element "
"in the calling DataFrame, if ``cond`` is ``False`` the element is used; "
"otherwise the corresponding element from the DataFrame ``other`` is used."
msgstr ""
"mask 方法是 if-then 用法的一种应用。对于调用 DataFrame 中的每个元素，如果"
" ``cond`` 为 ``False``，则使用该元素；否则使用 DataFrame ``other`` 中对应"
"的元素。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.where.where:36 of
msgid ""
"The signature for :func:`DataFrame.where` differs from "
":func:`numpy.where`. Roughly ``df1.where(m, df2)`` is equivalent to "
"``np.where(m, df1, df2)``."
msgstr ""
":func:`DataFrame.where` 的签名与 :func:`numpy.where` 不同。大致上 ``df1."
"where(m, df2)`` 等价于 ``np.where(m, df1, df2)``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.where.where:40 of
msgid ""
"For further details and examples see the ``mask`` documentation in "
":ref:`indexing <indexing.where_mask>`."
msgstr ""
"更多详情和示例请参见 :ref:`indexing <indexing.where_mask>` 中的 ``mask`` "
"文档。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.where.where:44 of
msgid "示例"
